---
title: Double Cheese & Pork Sausage Flatbreads with Roasted Long Green Pepper & Onion
description: In our humble opinion, flatbreads > pizza, any day! We know that may sound blasphemous, but stick with us. First of all, the golden, crispy crust is a veritable blank canvas. It’s not beholden to simply marinara and mozz! In fact, ours is topped with rich tomato sauce, sweet roasted pepper slices, savory pork sausage, and TWO kinds of cheese. Can your ’za do that?! Yeah, we didn’t think so.
